{"tid":1582564,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聽日要何妖輸出革命同十四億人攪炒！！！","createTime":"2019-09-20T06:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T16:20:02.000Z","uid":238693,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f5f2846cb0c1579d510a2b5974ab902cbd8c9699","tid":1582564,"uid":238693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T06:46:45.000Z","msg":"何妖同馬迷攬炒之後再下一城，聽日班馬要搞連儂牆，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地要佢同毛主席攬炒</span>！<br />\n方法好簡單，一滴血都唔駛流<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tdsw0rh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftdsw0rh.jpg&h=5952fe5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位今晚一齊將連儂牆改裝「毛牆」，毛澤東早年大把精彩說話，認識中國歷史嘅都知佢真係靠文宣贏江山！</span>（嗱戴頭盔先，我就唔夠膽提「湘獨」、「各省人民自決主義」、「二十二行省三特區兩藩地，合共二十七個地方，最好分為二十七國」呢啲咁毒辣嘅嘢啦）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n毛牆當眼位要好似隻揪sir 大埔連儂隧道咁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">整大大個毛主席死人頭！如果佢地敢拆，呢個畫面一定震驚十四億同胞</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMXH695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMXH695.jpg&h=73667be6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起都興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足一齊等睇好戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7f0c46adf511e2bfcc378a9c3f22529690033f","tid":1582564,"uid":27918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"[<strong><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">加拿大撚入</span></strong></strong>] <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>第一次</ins></span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins>海外</ins></span><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>大型</ins></span><span style=\"color: red;\">籌款</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">(好似係)<